{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_ovh4dezfdoqk0zih2j35jr","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"717438524","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/private/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/claude-code/2026-07-21T17-57-52-415Z/caveman-docs-from-code-3/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","content":"# Cache API\n\nThe Cache API provides an in-memory key-value store using a Map under the hood.\n\n## createCache()\n\nCreates a new cache instance with the following methods:\n\n```js\nfunction createCache() {\n  return { get, set, delete, clear }\n}\n```\n\nReturns a new cache object with `get`, `set`, `delete`, and `clear` methods.\n\n## Methods\n\n### get(key)\n\nRetrieves the value associated with the given key.\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `key`: The key to look up.\n\n**Returns:** The stored value or `undefined` if not found.\n\n### set(key, value)\n\nStores a value under the given key.\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `key`: The key to store the value under.\n- `value`: The value to store.\n\n**Returns:** The stored value.\n\n### delete(key)\n\nRemoves the entry for the given key.\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `key`: The key to delete.\n\n**Returns:** `true` if the key was found and deleted, `false` otherwise.\n\n### clear()\n\nRemoves all entries from the cache.\n\n**Returns:** `undefined`\n"}}],"model":"qwen/qwen3.5-9b","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6219,"output_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":6107},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"13266f67-fceb-494e-880f-d06caee3fb8e","uuid":"6380ad6c-fbd5-4bdf-8364-9fad254763fb","timestamp":"2026-07-22T02:07:51.584Z"}
